# .graphifyignore - extra excludes for `graphify` knowledge-graph scans of this repo.
# gitignore syntax. This is an ADDITIVE exclude list (not the zero-trust .gitignore allowlist).
#
# graphify's engine already prunes node_modules, .venv/venv, dist, build, target,
# __pycache__, .ruff_cache, .next/.nuxt/.turbo, graphify-out, and .worktrees via its
# built-in _SKIP_DIRS - do NOT re-list those here. Below: repo-specific generated trees
# the engine WOULD otherwise pick up as source.
#
# NOTE: graphify's `**/` does not match repo-root-level files; use the slash-less
# `*.ext` form, which gitignore matches at every depth (root included).

# Bundled connector archives. Defense-in-depth only: .mcpb is not a recognized source
# type, so the engine already skips it - this just makes the intent explicit.
*.mcpb

# Generated audit + runtime outputs (this program writes here; not architecture)
docs/audits/
docs/.run/

# SDD progress ledgers (process state, not codebase)
.superpowers/

# Minified/generated JS
*.min.js
